{"tid":247584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港絕對係2線城市","createTime":"2017-05-18T02:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T02:52:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6183530d53b64abef07fdaa09a5f1c9615cbc3cc","tid":247584,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:22:14.000Z","msg":"你班5毛講就係?<br />\n香港係國際一線城市,全球公認,支那國咪繼續呃自己囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港2線?<br />\n上海,深圳咪3線,其他省會咪4,5線?<br />\n你都忽忽地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你係要話一個男人,係女人來,無意思的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跪求你地支那國有個國際城市出現啦<br />\n等左15年,頸都長了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08620802099e21bfb29fd64d1a4fa77e26761ce7","tid":247584,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:23:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0fc09988b740dfb4eb9ba1673d438730078bc71","tid":247584,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:24:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7490cd251f59814f75730aebbbcb7478c362cd3","tid":247584,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 腥港"},{"pid":"9b638c9b829306bd9a40923405237f757342952c","tid":247584,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排瑞士個排名話香港競爭力第一 而支那排名話香港競爭力係中國排名第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那國報告全球不受認,我睇過2個,得淡笑<br />\n<br />\n例子1報告<br />\n話福田樓價要超香港<br />\n佢個報告係用福田最高單成交,同 天水圍&amp;深水埗 平均呎價比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後話自己已經貴過香港<br />\n<br />\n例子2報告<br />\n深圳收入超香港<br />\n香港利得稅收16.5%(仲有退稅),支那國收33%,仲有大把未浮面稅唔計,<br />\n咁都只係勁香港少少,高下立見了"},{"pid":"2aa57aaa3364dedec04f4b9975f8107a48ca8cce","tid":247584,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:33:24.000Z","msg":"Mori Memorial Foundation 有個Global Power City Index可以參考吓，香港第七，不過唔見中國城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mori-m-foundation.or.jp/img/ius_gpci2016_map.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmori-m-foundation.or.jp%2Fimg%2Fius_gpci2016_map.jpg&h=5315a4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"http://mori-m-foundation.or.jp/english/ius2/gpci2/index.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmori-m-foundation.or.jp%2Fenglish%2Fius2%2Fgpci2%2Findex.shtml&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5d491568\" target=\"_blank\">http://mori-m-foundation.or.jp/english/ius2/gpci2/index.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"dc5eb20c1b3d9f77f68b8b6e899dca3c90850ed6","tid":247584,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mori Memorial Foundation 有個Global Power City Index可以參考吓，香港第七，不過唔見中國城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mori-m-foundation.or.jp/img/ius_gpci2016_map.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmori-m-foundation.or.jp%2Fimg%2Fius_gpci2016_map.jpg&h=5315a4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"http://mori-m-foundation.or.jp/english/ius2/gpci2/index.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmori-m-foundation.or.jp%2Fenglish%2Fius2%2Fgpci2%2Findex.shtml&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5d491568\" target=\"_blank\">http://mori-m-foundation.or.jp/english/ius2/gpci2/index.shtml</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以支那國呃自己無意思 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870d01e6a0734a531fb585922512987dcad2583d","tid":247584,"uid":23848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:52:18.000Z","msg":"是但啦 最好變做10線，咪搞香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}